<plot>Clearview is the drama about a missing person case which has detectives scrambling to find the pregnant wife of an uncaring husband. When all avenues fail, a psychic tries to help. Detective Rojas and Detective Serra seek out all options including Ruth and Paul, a husband wife team who are the only ones providing clues. Ruth is having visions of the crime and Paul is convinced she can find the girl before she runs out of time.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?108490</url></doc>
